{"tid":1359681,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"周杰倫出道20周年「嘉年華」(與他的朋友) 世界巡迴演唱會","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:55:05.000Z","uid":2207,"like":11,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc4f2c6b04bc0009e01c293f2e6a7f76ff148cf","tid":1359681,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:44:37.000Z","msg":"唔知今次啲歌會低幾多個key<br />\n有幾多首經典比啲朋友仔唱<br />\n唱到第幾句就 「一齊來」呢 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd121a2a3dcae2b6a3832b72b906383c5ba22b8e","tid":1359681,"uid":9726,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c2d416bf54ed7b938ed4f1c05af95363ac0b7b1","tid":1359681,"uid":67238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"(嚴禁罵戰) 睇到周杰倫依家既LIVE真係好心痛...<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/596813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/596813</a><br />\n<br />\n大家睇完我呢個post先決定買唔買飛啦 如果真係die hard fans既話 勸你唔好帶非fans朋友去喇 廢事害人"},{"pid":"db6c038af1e42cf182b8678bfb8d52511783e4ee","tid":1359681,"uid":4462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"全場都唱園遊會"},{"pid":"1f1cf06f510101ce2e46153c60fd4a234526c73b","tid":1359681,"uid":2207,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3c2d416bf54ed7b938ed4f1c05af95363ac0b7b1","tid":1359681,"uid":67238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"(嚴禁罵戰) 睇到周杰倫依家既LIVE真係好心痛...<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/596813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/596813</a><br />\n<br />\n大家睇完我呢個post先決定買唔買飛啦 如果真係die hard fans既話 勸你唔好帶非fans朋友去喇 廢事害人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"完全明白，真fan 真係會好心痛<br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n我聽返佢2004 個演唱會<br />\n我仲係會驚歎，仲係會感動<br />\n因為佢用盡全力表演，好有誠意去呈現佢既音樂<br />\n<br />\nfan 唔係因為佢有肌肉鍾意佢<br />\n唔係因為佢識打波鍾意佢<br />\n唔係因為佢識魔術鍾意佢<br />\n唔係因為佢拍戲鍾意佢<br />\n<br />\n係因為音樂呀！<br />\n<br />\n點解佢可以放棄哂音樂，創作<br />\n放棄埋自己<br />\n<br />\n明明係一個天才<br />\n最後都會變哂質<br />\n<br />\n如果佢仲愛音樂既<br />\n根本就唔會容許自己咁差。<br />\n<br />\n對佢呢一兩年完全因為錢而搞演唱會既心態<br />\n我唔會睇喇<br />\n對唔住。"},{"pid":"6ffb37d3541bc2b67a42f2c64e876c7ce307756b","tid":1359681,"uid":196752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"超時代果陣時先得小學 第一次睇已經係魔天倫一 尾場(佢同EASON 果場 諗起都仲覺得好正)<br />\n地表一二仲加埋睇左四場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> HEA左好多 把聲又一年比一年虛 氣息又唔掂<br />\n唔期望 今次會有無與倫比 07 超時代質素 <br />\n但唔該至少俾番魔天倫質素我丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:死忠 應該點都去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終太多回憶"},{"pid":"564b9db21fd5beff78194397ee080b15d025874a","tid":1359681,"uid":2207,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6ffb37d3541bc2b67a42f2c64e876c7ce307756b","tid":1359681,"uid":196752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"超時代果陣時先得小學 第一次睇已經係魔天倫一 尾場(佢同EASON 果場 諗起都仲覺得好正)<br />\n地表一二仲加埋睇左四場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> HEA左好多 把聲又一年比一年虛 氣息又唔掂<br />\n唔期望 今次會有無與倫比 07 超時代質素 <br />\n但唔該至少俾番魔天倫質素我丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:死忠 應該點都去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終太多回憶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T01:19:07.000Z","msg":"我本身繼續去睇都係因為回憶呢兩個字<br />\n不過之後再諗深一層 ..<br />\n佢成個演唱會都係hea 到仆街黎開<br />\n真係唔值得盲比錢佢<br />\n因為佢而家100%係因為錢字而開<br />\n<br />\n我覺得 ..演唱會唔係要整隻高達, 整架戰機, 放幾百個煙花,<br />\n或者用幾千萬去整效果叫做正,<br />\n一個結他, 一個琴<br />\n認真咁唱先係大家想要既野<br />\n<br />\n回憶? 只係屬於我地<br />\n當我地既回憶諗住入場聽返佢唱<br />\n但係變哂大合唱, 比哂佢d 朋友唱半首<br />\n仲叫回憶咩? 佢有珍惜我地既回憶咩?"},{"pid":"dcfbebdd4a8c2ca0e8eda0438dcc751ec5eae357","tid":1359681,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"出新歌未呀屌佢"},{"pid":"3d1a49f60293360fec81b27f5c440cb6ab174125","tid":1359681,"uid":172677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ffb37d3541bc2b67a42f2c64e876c7ce307756b","tid":1359681,"uid":196752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:54:24.000Z","msg":"超時代果陣時先得小學 第一次睇已經係魔天倫一 尾場(佢同EASON 果場 諗起都仲覺得好正)<br />\n地表一二仲加埋睇左四場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> HEA左好多 把聲又一年比一年虛 氣息又唔掂<br />\n唔期望 今次會有無與倫比 07 超時代質素 <br />\n但唔該至少俾番魔天倫質素我丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:死忠 應該點都去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終太多回憶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"我記得第一次聽佢係回到過去開始 <br />\n第一次聽佢演唱會係魔天倫草蜢個場<br />\n你eason個場好似提早左開 因為打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我無聽過地表最強<br />\n去兩次都係魔天倫1同2"},{"pid":"c0eb53dc357406a9035706a0867f14a02643275b","tid":1359681,"uid":706,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"細個無錢睇<br />\n大個左終於有得睇，睇完，真係失望到仆街<br />\n仲hea撚過我唱k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班朋友又廢又柒<br />\n無眼睇"},{"pid":"16e0219e57fc6daca0c134c80d2bacbb4c9d0c93","tid":1359681,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"上一次個演唱會叫好朋友演唱會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728d041b97ca303dac32d13ba48c6dc2e06a83bf","tid":1359681,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:03:08.000Z","msg":"又大型ktv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" cla